</tr>
<tr>
<td><a href="CPU" title="CPU" class="mw-redirect">Processor</a></td>
<td colspan="2"><a href="MOS_Technology" title="MOS Technology">MOS Technology</a> <a href="MOS_Technology_6502" title="MOS Technology 6502">6502A</a> at 2 <a href="Megahertz" title="Megahertz" class="mw-redirect">MHz</a></td>
